Sentencas: Yttria-stabilized zirconia films have been deposited onto doped ceria discs for fuel cell applications, The deposition is achieved by hydrolysis-assisted pyrolysis reactions in a low-pressure reactor.
Titulo: Metal-organic vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte layers for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Film cracking can be alleviated by reducing the substrate temperature continuously during deposition.
Titulo: Metal-organic vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte layers for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: A model analysis of the kinetic data provides insight into the nature of the hydrolysis-;assisted pyrolytic deposition reactions.
Titulo: Metal-organic vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte layers for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Compared with structures made by sputtering and the set-gel process, significant improvements in open-circuit voltages are observed.
Titulo: Metal-organic vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte layers for solid oxide fuel cell applications
